sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server
    Note right of browser: Request is sent with the payload
    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    Note over browser,server: In SPA there is no redirect.
    Note over browser,server: Only the part of HTML where changes occur, is done in the DOM itself.<br/>Thus no need of re-rendering the whole html document.
    server-->>browser: Only response message in console { message: 'note created' }
    deactivate server
